import folium  #  map visuals
import pandas as pd  #  data manipulation
import requests

crimeData = pd.read_csv("wibr.csv")[:1000] 
crimeData["Latitude"] = ""
crimeData["Longitude"] = ""
crimeData["type"] = 0

for index, row in crimeData.iterrows():
    try:
        address = str(row["Location"]) + ", Milwaulkee, WI"
        address = address.replace(" ", "+")
        r = requests.get("https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json?address={}&key=AIzaSyBU828rT3AJLuU4LtZksyB2iWH63oBLCsU".format(address))
        jsonInfo = r.json()
        locationDict = jsonInfo['results'][0]['geometry']['location']
        crimeData["Latitude"][index] = locationDict['lat']
        crimeData["Longitude"][index] = locationDict['lng']
        if (row["Theft"] != 0)| (row["VehicleTheft"] != 0)| (row["LockedVehicle"] != 0):
            crimeData["type"][index] = 1
        elif (row["CriminalDamage"] != 0) | (row["Burglary"] != 0):
            crimeData["type"][index] = 2
        elif  (row["AssaultOffense"] != 0) | (row["Robbery"]!= 0):
            crimeData["type"][index] = 3
        elif (row["Arson"] != 0) | (row["Homicide"] != 0) | (row["SexOffense"] != 0):
            crimeData["type"][index] = 4
        
    except IndexError:
        crimeData["Latitude"][index] = ""
        crimeData["Longitude"][index] = ""
        crimeData["type"][index] = ""

from folium.plugins import MarkerCluster

city_map = folium.Map(location=[43.0389, -87.9065],zoom_start=13)
mc = MarkerCluster().add_to(city_map)

for index, row in crimeData.iterrows():
    if (row["Latitude"] != ""):
        if (row["type"] == 1):
            folium.Marker(location=(row["Latitude"],row["Longitude"]), popup = "Theft",icon=folium.Icon(color='black', icon='remove'),).add_to(mc) 
        elif (row["type"] == 2):
            folium.Marker(location=(row["Latitude"],row["Longitude"]), popup = "Burglary & Damage",icon=folium.Icon(color='blue', icon='plus'),).add_to(mc) 
        elif (row["type"] == 3):
            folium.Marker(location=(row["Latitude"],row["Longitude"]), popup = "Assult & Robbery",icon=folium.Icon(color='pink', icon='user'),).add_to(mc) 
        elif (row["type"] == 4):
            folium.Marker(location=(row["Latitude"],row["Longitude"]), popup = "Sex offense & Homicide & Arson",icon=folium.Icon(color='red', icon='heart')).add_to(mc) 
city_map
